Engineers responsible for this project were:

* Michal Lesniewski (m.lesniewski@samsung.com)
Main ADBI developer. Developed version 1 and 2 and made heavy foundation for the current version no 3.

* Jakub Janeczko (j.janeczko@samsung.com)
Successive ADBI developer. Took over ADBI development after Michal's retirement from this project, evolved and concluded version 3. Finally ported ADBI for the ARM64 architecture.

* Bartosz Zator (b.zator@samsung.com)
Devised the ADBI idea, technically and organizationally managed the project throughout its history.
